com.foreach.across.core.context.configurer

Class ComponentScanConfigurer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.core.context.configurer.ApplicationContextConfigurerAdapter
      • com.foreach.across.core.context.configurer.ComponentScanConfigurer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ApplicationContextConfigurer

    public class ComponentScanConfigurer
extends ApplicationContextConfigurerAdapter
    Simple implementation for specifying packages an ApplicationContext should scan. Packages can be specified as String or by providing a Class in that package.
